    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Another option would be to split out two ranges: keep the parameter used for pathfinding at 8, but then reduce the one that prematurely cancels move orders that otherwise would get closer to the target location.  This is adding a hack on top of a hack, but all this logic needs to be ripped out at some point anyway, and it should improve the gameplay behaviour in the meantime."
